org.finra.jtaf.core.asserts
Class IgnoreErrorsAssert

java.lang.Object
  org.finra.jtaf.core.asserts.IgnoreErrorsAssert

public class IgnoreErrorsAssert
extends Object

This class is mainly a wrapper for Junits Assert class. Instead of immediately throwing an error, the error is stored in an ErrorAccumulator to be thrown when needed.
